author: nagy
msg: Fixed a problem with the RequestURIBasedDispatcher not being thread safe, as it relied upon non-synchronized instance variables even though the object is a singleton within the scope of an AxisConfiguration.  Since multiple threads may access the object at the same time, there was the potential for a message to be dispatched to the wrong service/operation.
